default: 100

Master 0-100 = 50

BGM 0 - 10 = 50 * 0.5 = 25

BGM volume adjust = 25
children.name: masterVolume

children.memo:
volume adustement between the current precentage for BGM

default: 1

1 = 100% volume
0.9 = 90% volume
0.8 = 80% volume
etc
0 = 0% volume

children.memo:

default: 1

0.9 = 90% volume
0.8 = 80% volume
etc
0 = 0% volume
